	dprr:hasNoteText "Tr. Pl. ? 49? See MRR 2.259; Wiseman, CQ 14, 1964, 129; NM 256-257, no. 363. Wiseman suggests that since other known Rubrii were enemies of Caesar, the author of the Lex Rubria should be identified with L. Rubrius (12) of Casinum.\n" .
